items.title: Nvidia, Salesforce, & HP earnings, Fed minutes: What to watch
items.description: Wednesday, May 28, will be a big one for Wall Street. Nvidia (NVDA) will report its first quarter earnings after the market close. Salesforce (CRM), HP (HPQ), and Abercrombie & Fitch (ANF) are also set to report their quarterly results. Also in focus will be the minutes from the FOMC meeting earlier this month. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.

items.title: Salesforce to acquire Informatica for $8 billion in latest AI push
items.description: Salesforce says the acquisition will help the San Francisco software company, which provides tools to help businesses manage sales and customer data, ramp up its AI efforts.
